title: Longhorn Invitational Wraps Up Fall Season for @OspreyWGolf
text: Longhorn Invitational Wraps Up Fall Season for @OspreyWGolf Story Links Live Scoring AUSTIN, Texas -- The North Florida women's golf team closes out its fall season tournament schedule beginning action Monday in the Betsy Rawls Longhorn Invitational at the UT Golf Club (par 72 / 6,298 yards).The Longhorn Invitational features a competitive 14-team field that includes four squads currently ranked in the Top 25 of the Golfstat rankings. No. 8 Kent State tops the list of ranked teams which also includes No. 22 UNLV, No. 24 Houston and No. 25 New Mexico.The Ospreys, who will be playing their second tournament in the last week, send a veteran lineup to the Longhorn Invitational led by a quartet of seniors.
